---
title: Swedish-Pork Meatballs & Cherry Sauce with Creamy Bacon-Herb Sauce, Garlicky Greens & Cheesy Mash
description: With two kinds of proteins: juicy pork and crispy bacon in the creamy sauce, these Swedish meatballs are pure comfort food.
Add a cheesy mash, with tart cherry sauce and greens and you'll have a dish paying homage to the true Scandi spirit.

